lead_paragraph: Former England coach Stuart Lancaster might be forgiven a wry smile on seeing Eddie Jones's first match squad as his successors' brave new world kicked off with a feeling of evolution rather than revolution.

headline.print_headline: Rugby-Jones Avoids Revolutionary Route to Scotland
